import { Navigate, Outlet, Route, Routes } from "react-router-dom";
import { PageTitle } from "../../../../_metronic/layout/core";
import { ChungNhanThucHanhCoSo } from "./chung-nhan-thuc-hanh-co-so/ChungNhanThucHanhCoSo";
import { HoatDongChuyenMon } from "./hoat-dong-chuyen-mon/HoatDongChuyenMon";
import { HoiDong } from "./hoi-dong/HoiDong";
import { LoaiHinhKinhDoanh } from "./loai-hinh-kinh-doanh/LoaiHinhKinhDoanh";
import { NoiTotNghiep } from "./noi-tot-nghiep/NoiTotNghiep";
import { PhamViHoatDongKinhDoanh } from "./pham_vi_hoat_dong_kinh_doanh/PhamViHoatDongKinhDoanh";
import { ThanhPhanHoSo } from "./thanh-phan-ho-so/ThanhPhanHoSo";
import { ThuTuc } from "./thu-tuc/ThuTuc";
import { VanBangChuyenMon } from "./van-bang-chuyen-mon/VanBangChuyenMon";
import { ViTriHanhNghe } from "./vi-tri-hanh-nghe/ViTriHanhNghe";

const usersBreadcrumbs = [
  {
    title: "Danh mục",
    path: "/admin/danh-muc/loai-hinh-kinh-doanh",
    isSeparator: false,
    isActive: false,
  },
  {
    title: "",
    path: "",
    isSeparator: true,
    isActive: false,
  },
];

const DanhMucPage = () => {
  return (
    <Routes>
      <Route element={<Outlet />}>
        <Route
          path="loai-hinh-kinh-doanh"
          element={
            <>
              <PageTitle breadcrumbs={usersBreadcrumbs}>
                Loại hình kinh doanh
              </PageTitle>
              <LoaiHinhKinhDoanh />
            </>
          }
        />
        <Route
          path="noi-tot-nghiep"
          element={
            <>
              <PageTitle breadcrumbs={usersBreadcrumbs}>
                Nơi tốt nghiệp
              </PageTitle>
              <NoiTotNghiep />
            </>
          }
        />

        <Route
          path="hoi-dong"
          element={
            <>
              <PageTitle breadcrumbs={usersBreadcrumbs}>Hội đồng</PageTitle>
              <HoiDong />
            </>
          }
        />
        <Route
          path="van-bang-chuyen-mon"
          element={
            <>
              <PageTitle breadcrumbs={usersBreadcrumbs}>
                Văn bằng chuyên môn
              </PageTitle>
              <VanBangChuyenMon />
            </>
          }
        />
        <Route
          path="pham-vi-hoat-dong-kinh-doanh"
          element={
            <>
              <PageTitle breadcrumbs={usersBreadcrumbs}>
                Phạm vi hoạt động kinh doanh
              </PageTitle>
              <PhamViHoatDongKinhDoanh />
            </>
          }
        />
        <Route
          path="hoat-dong-chuyen-mon"
          element={
            <>
              <PageTitle breadcrumbs={usersBreadcrumbs}>
                Hoạt động chuyên môn
              </PageTitle>
              <HoatDongChuyenMon />
            </>
          }
        />
        <Route
          path="thanh-phan-ho-so"
          element={
            <>
              <PageTitle breadcrumbs={usersBreadcrumbs}>
                Thành phần hồ sơ
              </PageTitle>
              <ThanhPhanHoSo />
            </>
          }
        />
        <Route
          path="loai-hinh-kinh-doanh"
          element={
            <>
              <PageTitle breadcrumbs={usersBreadcrumbs}>
                Loại hình kinh doanh
              </PageTitle>
              <ThanhPhanHoSo />
            </>
          }
        />
        <Route
          path="chung-nhan-thuc-hanh-co-so"
          element={
            <>
              <PageTitle breadcrumbs={usersBreadcrumbs}>
                Chứng nhận thực hành cơ sở
              </PageTitle>
              <ChungNhanThucHanhCoSo />
            </>
          }
        />
        <Route
          path="noi-tot-nghiep"
          element={
            <>
              <PageTitle breadcrumbs={usersBreadcrumbs}>
                Nơi tốt nghiệp
              </PageTitle>
              <NoiTotNghiep />
            </>
          }
        />
        <Route
          path="vi-tri-hanh-nghe"
          element={
            <>
              <PageTitle breadcrumbs={usersBreadcrumbs}>
                Vị trí hành nghề
              </PageTitle>
              <ViTriHanhNghe />
            </>
          }
        />
        <Route
          path="thu-tuc"
          element={
            <>
              <PageTitle breadcrumbs={usersBreadcrumbs}>Thủ tục</PageTitle>
              <ThuTuc />
            </>
          }
        />
      </Route>

      <Route
        index
        element={<Navigate to="/admin/danh-muc/loai-hinh-kinh-doanh" />}
      />
    </Routes>
  );
};

export default DanhMucPage;
